Package: checktor
Title: Extra CRAN Checks for R Package Submissions
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("James Joseph", "Balamuta",
            email = "james.balamuta@gmail.com", 
            role = c("aut", "cre"),
            comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-2826-8458")
           )
    )
Description: Provides automated checks for common CRAN submission issues that 
    are not caught by standard 'R CMD check'. Based on the comprehensive 
    documentation of CRAN submission problems, this package helps package 
    maintainers identify and fix issues before submission, reducing rejection 
    rates and improving the submission process. Covers code issues, DESCRIPTION 
    file formatting, documentation problems, and general package structure 
    concerns. Think of it as a "doctor" for your R packages!
License: AGPL (>= 3)
URL: https://github.com/coatless-rpkg/checktor
